articles.title: ‘Indiana Jones’ Box Office: How ‘Dial of Destiny’ Compares to the 4 Previous Movies - Hollywood Reporter
articles.description: The fifth and final installment in the famed adventure-action series opened to $60.4 million in North America over the June 30-July 2 weekend, a troublesome outcome for a movie reportedly costing $295 million to make.
